name: EmergencyDepartmentVisit
title: Emergency Department Visit
description: This value set is redundant with the value set with OID 2.16.840.1.113883.3.117.1.7.1.292. For consistency purposes (and to reduce redundancy) use the value set with OID 2.16.840.1.113883.3.117.1.7.1.292 instead of using this value set. This value set is no longer maintained as of 09/29/2021.
purpose: (Clinical Focus: The purpose of this value set is to represent concepts for encounters in the emergency department.),(Data Element Scope: This value set may use a model element related to Encounter.),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes concepts that represent an encounter for care provided to new and established patients in the emergency department.),(Exclusion Criteria: Excludes concepts that represent an encounter not representative of ED visits, including critical care and observation services.)
